    },
    "section": "",
    "image": "",
    "answer": "b",
    "solution": "a = 5, d = 6, n = n\nSn = n/2(2a + (n-1)d)\n= n/2(2(5) + (n-1)6)\n= n/2(10 + 6n-6)\n= n/2(6n+4)\n= 6n2/2 + 4n/2\n= 32 + 2n\n= n(3n + 2)",
